---

This project is a thin configuration/loader layer that builds on, and depends
on, two third-party projects, each under their own license:

  - Kitten Scientists (https://github.com/kitten-science/kitten-scientists)
    Licensed under the MIT License. This project loads Kitten Scientists and
    applies configuration presets to it; it does not vendor or modify its
    source except for an optional pinned build kept in `vendor/` for offline
    use, which remains under its original MIT License.

  - Kittens Game by Nuclear Unicorn (https://kittensgame.com)
    The game this project helps automate. All game assets and code are the
    property of their respective authors. This project does not redistribute
    the game.
